#scriverner_RPG
---

A template for Scrivener to produce Role Playing Game (RPG) modules.

## Source
origionally developed by [Ricardo Signes](https://rjbs.manxome.org/rpg/) and presented here as a backup for development of that work.

### Origional
RPG Scrivener template (be aware the link is direct to the download)  [Here](https://rjbs.manxome.org/rpg/RPG-Campaign.scrivtemplate.gz)
